{"tid":2428446,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(袁大師又創新猷）：建議食肆設立「執枱專員」","createTime":"2021-03-01T14:21:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T14:50:09.000Z","uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a608131eebd11e0d8fdc883993286211ba4f4720","tid":2428446,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T14:21:49.000Z","msg":"近日 K11 Musea 商場的「名潮食館」爆發武漢肺炎感染群組，政府專家顧問袁國勇視察後指，餐廳茶水間同時放置使用過和乾淨的餐具，或造成交叉感染，又指過去半年一直建議食肆設立「執枱專員」。<br />\n<br />\n食環署副署長黃淑嫻今（3 月 1 日）表示，已與餐飲業界開會，要求業界安排「執枱專員」，專責收拾使用後的餐桌，或確保員工執枱後須使用酒精搓手液、更換手套，措施將納入本星期四起生效的防疫規例。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%A3%9F%E8%82%86%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9B%E8%B5%B7%E9%A0%88%E8%A8%AD-%E5%9F%B7%E6%9E%B1%E5%B0%88%E5%93%A1-4-%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%89%8D%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84-%E6%8F%9B%E6%B0%A3%E7%8E%87-%E6%AF%8F%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91-6-%E6%AC%A1/?fbclid=IwAR3wRCp0_nDo2qdfRDsSwr177YTHoQBa9eSOKD727HQ1NqPm09msuJ8_LJo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E9%25A3%259F%25E8%2582%2586%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%259B%259B%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E9%25A0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AD-%25E5%259F%25B7%25E6%259E%25B1%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%2593%25A1-4-%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25BA%2595%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%2596%2584-%25E6%258F%259B%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E7%258E%2587-%25E6%25AF%258F%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25B0%2591-6-%25E6%25AC%25A1%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3wRCp0_nDo2qdfRDsSwr177YTHoQBa9eSOKD727HQ1NqPm09msuJ8_LJo&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt1wb0NiVgWGuYP6yHf6H5SmE%3D&h=aa6db5ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E9%25A3%259F%25E8%2582%2586%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%259B%259B%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E9%25A0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AD-%25E5%259F%25B7%25E6%259E%25B1%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%2593%25A1-4-%25E6%259C%2